last_episode_to_air.overview: Eliseo defends himself before a court of law so that he doesn't lose his business or face jailtime.

name: The Boss
overview: Eliseo is the superintendent of an upscale building. On the surface, is cordial and docile in his role, but underneath Eliseo believes himself the omnipotent figure of the community — meddling in the affairs of residents and pulling strings as he sees fit. Eliseo's only concern is protecting his job, which comes under threat by a proposed pool project.

episodes.name: A Dangerous Project
episodes.overview: Superintendent Eliseo learns about a project that would result in him losing his home and job.

episodes.name: A Sympathetic Move
episodes.overview: Eliseo manipulates a case of infidelity and plays on a woman's faith in a bid to secure allies.

episodes.name: A Tourist in Buenos Aires
episodes.overview: Eliseo must run off a Swiss tourist after the owners of the apartment he rented her return early.

episodes.name: A Lover for Zambrano
episodes.overview: Eliseo employs drastic measures to destroy his adversary's marriage.

episodes.name: Surprise Visit
episodes.overview: The arrival of a suspicious character at the condominium forces Eliseo to investigate.

episodes.name: Night Driver
episodes.overview: Eliseo is ensnared in a blackmail scheme by the daughter of a menacing union leader.

episodes.name: Therapeutic Companion
episodes.overview: After efforts to help a tenant's depressed son backfires, Eliseo tries to undo the good he's done.

episodes.name: Sabotage in the Engine Room
episodes.overview: Eliseo's latest plan to derail the pool project plunges the building into a dark chaos.

episodes.name: The Squatter in 5B
episodes.overview: Eliseo digs deep into his bag of deception to secure the three votes needed to block the project.

episodes.name: The Moment of Truth
episodes.overview: A last-minute betrayal allows the passing of the pool project, sending Eliseo into a dark place.

episodes.name: The Phoenix
episodes.overview: Eliseo returns to the building during an emergency that transforms him into a hero.

episodes.name: A Woman of Solidarity
episodes.overview: The arrival of a new neighbor to the building jeopardizes all of Eliseo's achievements.

episodes.name: An Unexpected Alliance
episodes.overview: Eliseo and Zambrano join forces and infiltrate Lucila's NGO to sabotage it.

episodes.name: Just a Little Scare
episodes.overview: Eliseo recruits his nephew Maxi to stage a fake robbery to scare Lucila away.

episodes.name: The Last Goodbye
episodes.overview: An unexpected death leaves Eliseo and the consortium devastated.

episodes.name: Surprise Occurrence
episodes.overview: Eliseo runs for the Board of Owners.

episodes.name: Medical Assessment
episodes.overview: Eliseo faces a psychiatric examination that threatens to expose his complex psyche.

episodes.name: Olives for Everyone
episodes.overview: Eliseo goes on a rural expedition to learn more about Lucila's secret past.

episodes.name: The Convention
episodes.overview: Eliseo attends a convention and decides what his next professional move will be.

episodes.name: Basurto Integrated Solutions
episodes.overview: Eliseo puts into motion his plan to take over all the buildings in the neighborhood.

episodes.name: Well Then...
episodes.overview: Eliseo faces some detractors. A surprise visitor stirs up his troubled and painful past.

episodes.name: A Second Chance
episodes.overview: Eliseo decides to immerse himself into tantric meditation to help him complete his next mission.

episodes.name: A Peck on the Lips
episodes.overview: An old enemy from Eliseo's past resurfaces.

episodes.name: Supercide
episodes.overview: Eliseo must take over one more building to have full control and comes up with a master plan.

episodes.name: Eliseo Versus the Argentine State
episodes.overview: Eliseo defends himself before a court of law so that he doesn't lose his business or face jailtime.
